WEBVTT

00:04.000 --> 00:05.000
You're a Mason?

00:05.000 --> 00:08.000
Sic transit gloria mundi!

00:08.000 --> 00:11.000
I love you, more than
anyone I've ever known.

00:11.000 --> 00:12.000
Well, that's enough for me.

00:12.000 --> 00:14.000
Yes, but I'm not in a position
to promise you anything.

00:14.000 --> 00:17.000
Father, I'm afraid I'm going
to need some more money.

00:17.000 --> 00:18.490
- How much?
- 43,000.

00:18.491 --> 00:19.720
What?

00:20.000 --> 00:23.000
Natasha, this is
Prince Andrei Bolkonsky.

00:23.000 --> 00:28.000
May I request the pleasure of a
dance with your daughter Natalia?

00:28.000 --> 00:29.000
Of course.

00:29.000 --> 00:33.000
Go to her, don't let her
get away! Propose to her.

00:33.000 --> 00:34.000
I will.

